OL,6,FBut he does believe the island could
OL,7,Fbenefit from having a city: "It's
OL,8,Fabout bringing more status, more
OL,9,Freputation and more civic pride to the
OL,10,Fisland of Jersey."
OL,12,FHowever, in Guernsey, there does not
OL,13,Fappear to be much appetite for turning
OL,14,FSt Peter Port into a city.
OL,16,FThe town's Constable Jenny Tasker
OL,17,Fsaid: "We discussed it in the douzaine
OL,18,Fand we felt that it was totally
OL,19,Finappropriate for St Peter Port for
OL,20,Fseveral reasons.
