OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands apply to
OL,4,Cturn their towns into cities?
OL,6,FHistorically, cities were areas with
OL,7,Fcathedrals, but having one is no
OL,8,Flonger a requirement.
OL,10,FBirmingham was the first town to be
OL,11,Fgiven the city title, despite not
OL,12,Fhaving a cathedral in 1889.
OL,14,FClaire Wells is Douglas City Council
OL,15,FLeader and hopes the new status will
OL,16,Fhelp entice more people to the Isle of
OL,17,FMan: "If we get any opportunity to
OL,18,Fraise our profile, to encourage people
OL,19,Fto come over here, whether it be to
OL,20,Fwork or visit, we want to do
OL,21,Feverything we can.
